Package org.chenile.core.context

package org.chenile.core.context
The core Chenile exchange objects are defined here. Headers are defined here along with some constants for popular header names. Convenience methods to retrieve headers are also provided
  • Class

    ChenileExchange
    A bidirectional exchange that navigates between different Chenile Interceptors.
